title: Number of births in Sweden 2009 to 2019
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of births. In total the number of data points it has is 11.
In general Number of births has stayed the same over the Year.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2010 and 2011.
The highest Number of births, of value 117425.0 was reached at Year 2016
The lowest Number of births, of value 111770.0 was reported at Year 2011
